{"tid":1077232,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉屌 啱啱愛回家個呃人個方法 我都中過招","createTime":"2019-03-25T12:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T13:16:47.000Z","uid":78683,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcafdec94348142c991121429e052bcb0fabf53","tid":1077232,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"之前返返吓工 有個客話佢身上無錢 問我借20蚊搭車 我見佢咁慘 畀咗100 又叫我畀電話佢 話一有錢就畀返我 我話唔使 所以無畀電話佢 點知佢之後有返嚟 但無畀返錢我<br />\n<br />\n有次出地鐵站 有個大陸人話佢無錢食飯 見佢講到咁慘 諗住畀50 點知無散紙 拎咗100 我一拎出嚟 都未出聲 佢就搶咗去<br />\n<br />\n今日睇完愛回家 先知原來係呃人⋯"},{"pid":"efda2eddd4084aad27035dfc94f22413327c94c5","tid":1077232,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"肩肩原來咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d64ca0d7c64dc8e1d8a1b270a9b728f82e1594","tid":1077232,"uid":151065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"應該要黑住面行啲人唔會敢問你嘢"},{"pid":"6eaf175af650245cd4d2f575d0bde2ebc19595d5","tid":1077232,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"肩肩好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62490477319fb1d5f1f48bfe65d86a2594900d4c","tid":1077232,"uid":37746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:50:48.000Z","msg":"有個人問我借錢搭車 我見佢咁慘 俾咗5蚊佢 佢問我 咦？你唔係要上車啦咩？ 我話我等緊人 搞到佢要扮走冇得係嗰度呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acca0521786c98a4fbb686287372734c170440e7","tid":1077232,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efda2eddd4084aad27035dfc94f22413327c94c5","tid":1077232,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"肩肩原來咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"不嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d91bb9c3cb4a